{% extends "base.jinja" %}

{% block content %}
<div class="page default fluid-container bg-600">
  <div class="container home-page py-4 tx-600">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center text-center mt-4">
        <h1><b>Hosting music events don't have to be difficult.</b></h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center text-center mt-4">
        <p>
          Ever wanted to host a music event but do not know how? You have come to the right place, here we provide easy to understand procedures
